\id TIT - Biblica® Open New Luo Translation 2020 
\h Tito 
\toc1 Tito 
\toc2 Tito 
\toc3 Tit 
\mt1 Tito 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 An Paulo, ma jatich Nyasaye kendo ma jaote Yesu Kristo ema andikonu baruwani. Nyasaye ne oora mondo ajiw yie mar joma Nyasaye oyiero obed motegno, kendo mondo apuonjgi adiera mamiyo giluoro Nyasaye,  
\v 2 kuom geno yudo ngima mochwere, mane Nyasaye, ma ok riambi osesingore chon ni nomiwa.  
\v 3 Nyasaye ma Jawarwa ema nohulo wachne malongʼo e ndalo mane en owuon oketo, kendo nogolo chik ni an ema onego miya tich mar lando wachneno. 
\b  
\p  
\v 4 Ne Tito, wuoda mar adier kuom yie moriwowa e achiel: 
\b  
\p Ngʼwono gi kwe moa kuom Nyasaye Wuoro kod Kristo Yesu ma Jawarwa obed kodi. 
\b  
\s1 Tich momi Tito 
\p  
\v 5 Gima omiyo ne aweyi Krete ne en ni mondo irie gik moko mane odongʼ kapok atieko, kendo mondo iyier jodong kanisa e dala ka dala, kaka ne achiki ni itim.  
\v 6 Jaduongʼ kanisa nyaka bed ngʼat ma wach moro amora marach onge kuome, kendo ngʼatno man-gi dhako achiel, ngʼat ma nyithinde oyie kendo ma ok nyal kwan kaka nyithindo maricho kendo ma wigi tek.  
\v 7 Nikech jatend kanyakla mar jo-Kristo en ngʼat marito tich Nyasaye, omiyo nyaka obed ngʼat ma wach moro amora marach onge kuome. Kik obed ngʼat mamiyo kanyakla mar joma oyie tingʼ mapek. Bende kik obed ngʼat mochayo ji kata ma ja-mirima, kata ngʼat mamer gi kongʼo, kata ngʼat mohero dhawo, kata ngʼat moyudo mwandu e yor mibadhi.  
\v 8 To nyaka obed ngʼat mohero rwako welo, mohero gigo mabeyo, ngʼat ma terore mos, ma ja-ratiro, moluoro Nyasaye; kendo mawinjo puonj.  
\v 9 Nyaka omak motegno puonj migeno, mana kaka osepuonje e kinde motelo, mondo eka ojiw joma moko gi puonj madier kendo okwer joma kwedo puonjno. 
\p  
\v 10 Nikech nitie ji mangʼeny ma jongʼanyo, ma gin mana jothor wach kendo jowuond ji, to moloyo jogo moter nyangu ma gin jo-Yahudi moyie.  
\v 11 Jogi nyaka kwer mondo olingʼ, nikech giketho mier mangʼeny ka gipuonjo gik ma ok owinjore gipuonji; kendo gitimo kamano mana mondo giyudie ohala ma ok nikare.  
\v 12 Kata mana janabi moro ma margi owuon osewacho niya, “Jo-Krete riambo kinde duto, gin ondiegi malich ma timbegi richo kendo gin jowuoro ma budho abudha.”  
\v 13 Wach janabigino en adier. Omiyo kwergi matek mondo eka gibed gi yie mar adier,  
\v 14 kendo mondo kik gichik itgi ni sigendini mag jo-Yahudi kata ni chike mag joma odagi adiera.  
\v 15 Gik moko duto ler mana ni jomaler, to kuom joma okethore ma ok oyie to onge gima ler. Chutho, pachgi kaachiel gi chunygi monego onyisgi kethogi osetho.  
\v 16 Giwacho ni gingʼeyo Nyasaye to gikwedo Nyasaye nogo gi timbegi manono. Gin acheje ma wigi tek kendo ok ginyal timo gimoro amora maber. 
\c 2  
\s1 Puonj kuom jo-Kristo 
\p  
\v 1 Nyaka ipuonj weche mowinjore gi puonj ma adiera.  
\v 2 Puonj jodongo mondo obed joma obidhore, ma ok ohero oyuma, kendo moritore, bende man-gi yie mar adier gihera kod kinda. 
\p  
\v 3 Kamano bende puonj mon madongo mondo kit ngimagi obed ranyisi maber, ma ok jokuoth, kata joma ohero madho kongʼo, to nyaka gibed gi puonj mabeyo.  
\v 4 Ka gitimo kamano, to ginyalo puonjo mon matindo kaka onego giher chwogi gi nyithindgi;  
\v 5 ka giterore mos kendo gidak e ngima maler bende ka girito e utegi. Nyaka gibed mon mangʼwon kendo moluoro chwogi mondo kik ngʼato angʼata yany wach Nyasaye. 
\p  
\v 6 Kamano bende onego ijiw yawuowi matindo mondo oritre.  
\v 7 Bednegi ranyisi e yore duto kitimo gik mabeyo. Kipuonjo to nyis ni in ngʼama ngimane oriere tir kendo ma ok dwar oyuma,  
\v 8 wecheni obed weche mowinjore ma ngʼato ok nyal chayo ni gin weche mofuwo mondo joma ok oyie kodi wigi okuodi nikech gionge gimoro amora marach ma ginyalo wacho kuomwa. 
\p  
\v 9 Puonj wasumbini mondo owinj ruodhi mag-gi e weche duto, kendo gitem timonegi mana gik malongʼo ma ok gidwokore kodgi,  
\v 10 kata kik gikwal gigegi, to ginyisre ni gin joma inyalo geno e weche duto mondo omi e yore duto gimi puonj mar Nyasaye Jawarwa oywa ji. 
\p  
\v 11 Nikech ngʼwono mar Nyasaye makelo warruok osefwenyore ne ji duto.  
\v 12 Ngʼwonono puonjowa mondo wakwed timbe maricho kod gombo mochido mag piny, kendo mondo wabed kawaritore e ngima makare mamiyo Nyasaye duongʼ e kindeni,  
\v 13 kapod warito geno mogwedhi ma en fwenyruok man-gi duongʼ mar Nyasacha maduongʼ kod Jawarwa, Yesu Kristo,  
\v 14 mane ochiworenwa mondo oreswa wawe timbe maricho kendo mondo opwodh ne en owuon joma owinjore bedo joge, moikore timo gik mabeyo. 
\p  
\v 15 Koro magi e gik monego ipuonji. Jiw ji kendo ikwergi gi teko duto. Kik iwene ngʼato thuolo mondo ochayi. 
\c 3  
\s1 Timbe mabeyo 
\p  
\v 1 Par ne ji mondo ochiw luor ne jotelo. Nyisgi mondo giwinj chik kendo mondo gibed moikore ne timo gimoro amora maber,  
\v 2 kik giketh nying ngʼato angʼata, gibed joma ohero kwe, kendo ma paro mar konyo jowetegi, ka ginyiso muolo madier ne ji duto. 
\p  
\v 3 Nikech wan bende chon ne wan joma ofuwo ma ok winj wach kendo wasumbini mag kit gombo gi mor mayoreyore mag ringruok. Ngimawa mapile nopongʼ gi ichlit gi nyiego; ka ji mon kodwa kendo wan bende onge winjruok e kindwa.  
\v 4 To kane ngʼwono kod hera mar Nyasaye ma Jawarwa ofwenyore to nowarowa.  
\v 5 Ne ok owarowa nikech tim moro makare mane wasetimo, to ne owarowa mana nikech ngʼwonone owuon. Nowarowa gi luok mane Roho Maler okelonwago ngima manyien kod nywol manyien.  
\v 6 Kuom Yesu Kristo ma Jawarwa Nyasaye noolonwa Roho mogundho,  
\v 7 mondo ka oseketwa kare kuom ngʼwonone to wabed jocham mwandune, ka wan gi geno mar yudo ngima mochwere.  
\v 8 Wachni en wach madiera. Kendo adwaro ni ijiw wechegi mondo joma oseketo genogi kuom Nyasaye otangʼ mondo gichiwre mar timo gik mabeyo. Gigi gin gik malongʼo chuth, kendo kelo konyruok ne ji duto. 
\p  
\v 9 To pogri gi mbekni mofuwo gi sigendini mag anywola gi mino wach kod dhawo kuom weche mag chike, nikech gik ma kamago ok kel konyruok kendo gionge tich.  
\v 10 Siem ngʼat makelo pogruok dichiel, to kisesiemo ngʼat makelo pogruok diriyo to pogri kode chuth.  
\v 11 Bed kingʼeyo gadiera ni ngʼama kamano en Jaricho ma pache okethore kendo en ngʼama ketho kongʼeyo. 
\b  
\s1 Weche Paulo mogik ne Timotheo 
\p  
\v 12 Bangʼe kaseoro Artemas kata Tukiko iri, to item matek mondo ibi ira piyo Nikopoli, nikech asechano mar bet kuno kinde chwiri.  
\v 13 Tim matek mondo ikony Zena ngʼat molony e chik kod Apolo e wuodhgi, kendo ne ni giyudo gik moko duto magidwaro. 
\b  
\p  
\v 14 Jowa nyaka puonjre keto chunygi kuom timo gik mabeyo, mondo eka giyud gik ma gikonyorego e ngimagi mapile kendo kik gidagi e ngima ma ok kel konyruok. 
\b  
\p  
\v 15 Ji duto man koda ooroni mos. 
\p Mosnwa joma oherowa kuom yie. 
\b  
\p Ngʼwono obed kodu uduto.